<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="content-type; content=text/html;">
    <title>LOGIN</title>
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="./style.css">
    <script>
        function setId() {
            var id = document.querySelector('#id_input').value;
            localStorage.setItem('id', id);
            location.href = '/'; 
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <head>
        <h1>LOGIN</h1>
    </head>
    <div role="main">
        <p>あなたのログインネームを入力してください。</p>
        <p>
            <input type="text" id="id_input">
            <button onclick="setId();">送信</button>
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>